Template: sacd-vfs/source_dir
Type: string
Default: /media/sacd
Description: Source directory containing SACD ISO files:
 Enter the path to the directory that contains your SACD ISO files.
 This directory will be overlaid with virtual folders for each ISO.

Template: sacd-vfs/mount_dir
Type: string
Default: /mnt/sacd
Description: Mount point for the SACD virtual filesystem:
 Enter the path where the virtual filesystem should be mounted.
 The directory will be created if it does not exist.

Template: sacd-vfs/run_user
Type: string
Default: root
Description: User to run the sacd-vfs service as:
 The systemd service will run as this user. Use 'root' for allow_other
 FUSE access, or a dedicated user if preferred.

Template: sacd-vfs/stereo
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Show stereo tracks?
 Enable this to expose the stereo area of each SACD disc.

Template: sacd-vfs/multichannel
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Show multichannel tracks?
 Enable this to expose the multichannel (surround) area of each SACD disc.
